Product description

Meta 739 Men's 30" iPad Consultation Coat

Meta Labwear

The Meta labcoat brand name has been a trusted leader since 1896 and continues to bring a perfect blend of style and function. Performance fabrics are used to provide features and benefits to round out the line designed to meet all of your labcoat needs.

  • Performance fabrics
  • Style and function
  • Wide size range

A TRUSTED LEADER

This consultation coat features a three-button closure, two lower outside iPad pockets, three inside pockets, one chest pocket, one hidden cell pocket, and front darts.

  • 65% Polyester, 35% Cotton Fine Line Twill with Soil Release
  • Three-button front closure
  • Two lower outside iPad pockets
  • Three inside pockets
  • One chest pockets and one hidden cell pocket
  • Front darts
  • Sizes: 32-56, 38L-56L

    I need this for clinical rotation in Chiropractic school. I will use it for about 1 year, so I didn't need anything too fancy. If I did, this wouldn't be the choice. It's all polyester and doesn't stretch and is very boxy in every dimension.

    After reading how to choose sizing, I went with 40, which is also the size suit coat I wear. It was much too small. The 42 fits well, but the arms are short. I usually perfectly fit into size Large clothing in most brands, but I had a hard time with this jacket as well as other cheaper lab coats.

    If you need something low cost, go with this and go one size up.
